[3] 仕様書:
-[[ISO/IEC 10744]]:1997
--[CSECTION[A.3.4.3 Architecture entity declaration]]
<http://www.y12.doe.gov/sgml/wg8/docs/n1920/html/clause-A.3.4.html#clause-A.3.4.3>
